description: Polaris Media ASA operates as a media house and printing company in Norway and Sweden. The company provides digital advertising services. It offers prints group and external newspapers, including editorial supplements and advertisement leaflets, civil prints, and other magazines/leaflets. In addition, the company distributes newspapers, as well as parcels, mail, and other product deliveries. Polaris Media ASA was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Trondheim, Norway.
